            <title>[SOLR-2626] ExternalFileField With Non-optimized Index</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2626</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The external file field in trunk works properly only with an optimized index.  If the index is not optimized incorrect values are used in function queries.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
